==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Substruct
<hw>Sub*struct"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Substruction</er>.]</ety> <def>To build beneath something; to lay as
the foundation.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He <qex>substructs</qex> the religion of Asia as the base.</q>
<rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Substruction</ent>⟦br⟧
